metadata.name: Crypto Archetype #1
metadata.description:
From the beginning of humanity, symbols have been creating the reality we experience and had shape the material world with their power, Gods, Demons, Spirits are entities that live in that symbolic reality sometimes called Archetypes. 
Today this entities had evolved into something more complex and powerful but they keep the same ability to shape humans reality, Web3 and crypto has become the place where they reside tempting the fool and helping to grow to the creative, the visionary and the builder. 
This collection represent some of this shapeshifter entities and their battle to conquer the imagination and the minds of humans.
